      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i need help understanding something that happened today. i was talking to my manager and something weird happened. every time he was being fake or hiding something, i felt this really sharp, vibrating tension in my chest, like the sound of his voice was hitting a weird frequency that didn't match what he was saying. it was almost like a physical dissonance. have you ever heard of people being able to sense that kind of thing? like a resonance shift?",
